Choi Hyun-suk!

48
00:02:31,351 --> 00:02:32,952
-It's great to see you.
-Yes.

49
00:02:33,019 --> 00:02:35,054
I hope he doesn't miss
an ingredient today.

50
00:02:35,121 --> 00:02:37,056
-Right?
-He won't, right?

51
00:02:37,123 --> 00:02:39,526
Yes, he's still the same.
He hasn't changed.

52
00:02:39,592 --> 00:02:41,161
-How good-looking.
-Yes.

53
00:02:41,227 --> 00:02:43,696
Hey, wait. This guy is here too?

54
00:02:43,763 --> 00:02:46,199
-Yes.
-I can't believe this.

55
00:02:46,266 --> 00:02:48,835
Wait, how did he secure his place?

56
00:02:48,902 --> 00:02:50,436
He's not just an amateur,

57
00:02:50,503 --> 00:02:52,172
