58
00:02:52,238 --> 00:02:55,808
The legend from the darkness, Kim Poong!

59
00:02:56,976 --> 00:02:58,278
The dark legend, Kim Poong.

60
00:02:58,344 --> 00:03:00,213
-The original Black Spoon.
-Yes.

61
