70
00:03:25,538 --> 00:03:27,106
Please come on out!

71
00:03:28,141 --> 00:03:29,475
Come on out!

72
00:03:30,176 --> 00:03:31,411
Come in! Come on out!

73
00:03:31,477 --> 00:03:32,345
COME AT ME

74
00:03:33,012 --> 00:03:35,882
THE 4 CHALLENGING CHEFS ARE HERE

75
00:03:35,949 --> 00:03:39,752
-Please come on out.
-Welcome.

76
00:03:39,819 --> 00:03:42,555
-My gosh. She's here too.
-The lineup is amazing.

77
00:03:42,622 --> 00:03:45,124
