-Yes.

78
00:03:45,191 --> 00:03:48,561
These are the challenging chefs
who are here to seize their victory.

79
00:03:48,628 --> 00:03:51,664
The winner of <i>Iron Chef</i>,

80
00:03:51,731 --> 00:03:53,933
the runner-up of <i>Culinary Class Wars</i>,

81
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,302
