-Please put the dishes up.

1194
00:50:53,784 --> 00:50:56,887
-I got the old dopamine rush again.
-Me too.

1195
00:50:56,953 --> 00:50:58,221
-It's so scary.
-The rush.

1196
00:50:58,288 --> 00:51:00,290
-Time flies.
-That was amazing.

1197
00:51:00,357 --> 00:51:03,693
