1199
00:51:05,862 --> 00:51:07,764
The dishes are complete.

1200
00:51:07,831 --> 00:51:09,499
Let's give them a round of applause.

1201
00:51:10,133 --> 00:51:13,270
-They were both on fire.
-Yes.

1202
