1235
00:52:36,553 --> 00:52:39,990
-The crab shell. Was it in there?
-He took out everything.

1236
00:52:40,056 --> 00:52:41,892
-He should've picked it out.
-It must've slipped in.

1237
00:52:41,958 --> 00:52:43,994
-Yes, he got the meat in a hurry.
-He took it all out.

1238
