1245
00:53:04,147 --> 00:53:06,249
-He's become eloquent.
-He has.

1246
00:53:06,316 --> 00:53:08,552
He's tasting the soup now.

1247
00:53:08,618 --> 00:53:09,553
The soup.

1248
00:53:10,387 --> 00:53:13,957
