1252
00:53:21,798 --> 00:53:23,600
Oh, no. Was it stiff?

1253
00:53:23,667 --> 00:53:25,702
-Was it stiff?
-Was the flour cake stiff?

1254
00:53:25,769 --> 00:53:28,605
