that I love so much.

1257
00:53:33,510 --> 00:53:37,347
-The soup is just wonderful.
-The soup.

1258
00:53:37,414 --> 00:53:39,649
It was sweet when I had it.
Is it okay now?

1259
00:53:39,716 --> 00:53:41,985
-It's all right now.
-He must've fixed it.

1260
00:53:42,052 --> 00:53:43,486
And as for the dumplings…

1261
00:53:43,553 --> 00:53:45,455
After all, he's the master.

1262
00:53:45,522 --> 00:53:49,659
The crunchiness of the dumpling
was wonderful.

1263
00:53:49,726 --> 00:53:51,361
You loved the crunch.

1264
00:53:51,428 --> 00:53:54,231
Overall, I thought it was on fire.

1265
00:53:54,297 --> 00:53:56,433
-Overall?
-Overall.

1266
00:53:57,467 --> 00:53:59,369
Yeon-bok's dish is on fire.

1267
00:53:59,436 --> 00:54:03,106
<i>Jingle, jingle, jingle, jingle, move aside</i>

1268
00:54:03,173 --> 00:54:05,875
<i>Jingle, jingle, jingle, jingle</i>

1269
00:54:05,942 --> 00:54:09,112
This time, he'll try Chef Mi-yeong's dish.

