-He'll try it first without rice.

1278
00:54:33,703 --> 00:54:35,372
I hope this gives him energy.

1279
00:54:35,438 --> 00:54:37,607
The spicy taste.

1280
00:54:37,674 --> 00:54:38,508
SAVORING

1281
00:54:38,575 --> 00:54:40,443
The spiciness is important.

1282
00:54:40,510 --> 00:54:43,847
It must be a bit salty.
He's eating rice right away.

1283
00:54:43,913 --> 00:54:46,049
He reaches for the rice right away.

1284
00:54:46,116 --> 00:54:49,552
