1287
00:54:55,959 --> 00:54:59,462
I hope it gives him energy.

1288
00:55:00,030 --> 00:55:03,199
<i>This is where Tak gets his power</i>

1289
00:55:03,266 --> 00:55:05,902
<i>It's where he really gets the power</i>

1290
00:55:05,969 --> 00:55:06,870
Gosh.

1291
00:55:06,936 --> 00:55:10,440
-The balance is perfect now.
-Did you find the balance?

1292
00:55:10,507 --> 00:55:11,341
Wasn't it a bit salty?

1293
00:55:11,408 --> 00:55:13,777
-Yes, it was a little salty.
-It was salty.

1294
00:55:13,843 --> 00:55:18,782
-The radish salad.
-She made it in just three, four minutes.

1295
00:55:20,016 --> 00:55:21,885
