-That's the thing.

1319
00:56:20,377 --> 00:56:23,046
The flour cake over there
felt like the rice over here.

1320
00:56:23,980 --> 00:56:25,849
-It's the time.
-Yes.

1321
00:56:25,915 --> 00:56:29,285
<i>Why did the rice come out from there?</i>

1322
00:56:29,352 --> 00:56:32,155
<i>Why was the rice undercooked?</i>

1323
00:56:33,490 --> 00:56:35,992
<i>Why was the rice undercooked?</i>

1324
00:56:36,059 --> 00:56:38,094
Both dishes had strengths and weaknesses.

1325
00:56:38,161 --> 00:56:40,230
Then, we'll taste

