Chef Yeon-bok's dish first.
This is Chef Yeon-bok's dish.

1327
00:56:44,434 --> 00:56:47,170
-It's called Bok Show.
-It smells good.

1328
00:56:47,237 --> 00:56:48,872
My gosh.

1329
00:56:48,938 --> 00:56:51,207
-This soup is…
-The soup.

1330
00:56:51,274 --> 00:56:54,477
I don't think
the flour cake was too hard for me.

1331
00:56:54,544 --> 00:56:55,912
-It wasn't too hard?
-No.

1332
00:56:55,979 --> 00:56:58,381
I like how tough it is.

1333
00:56:58,448 --> 00:56:59,549
