The side dishes were wonderful too.

1351
00:57:49,232 --> 00:57:51,835
-I rarely eat uncooked pepper.
-You don't?

1352
00:57:51,901 --> 00:57:55,171
-But it's great when it's seasoned.
-In doenjang.

1353
00:57:55,238 --> 00:58:01,277
Now, who will win the opening match
