1357
00:58:10,620 --> 00:58:12,355
Will it be Lee Yeon-bok or Lee Mi-yeong?

1358
00:58:13,289 --> 00:58:14,324
I pressed it.

1359
00:58:14,390 --> 00:58:18,962
We used ingredients
from Youngtak's fridge to hold…

1360
