Real Good Braised Octopus and Kimchi.

1373
00:58:57,333 --> 00:58:59,702
Which one did Youngtak choose?

1374
00:58:59,769 --> 00:59:00,803
The winner is…

1375
00:59:00,870 --> 00:59:02,071
Who is it?

1376
00:59:05,508 --> 00:59:06,676
Who is it?

1377
00:59:08,545 --> 00:59:11,414
Lee Yeon-bok! Chef Yeon-bok wins!

1378
00:59:11,481 --> 00:59:12,982
-Great job.
