You're an oil thief!

1901
01:20:17,512 --> 01:20:20,749
This is a battle between two alumni
of the same culinary college.

1902
01:20:20,816 --> 01:20:22,851
Look at that. That was amazing.

1903
01:20:22,918 --> 01:20:25,787
Ho-young is moving
much swifter than before.

1904
01:20:25,854 --> 01:20:27,889
-He's moving very slowly.
-He's so slow.

1905
01:20:27,956 --> 01:20:29,124
You have 30 seconds!

1906
01:20:29,191 --> 01:20:33,295
You can't do anything more.
You have 30 seconds!

1907
01:20:33,361 --> 01:20:34,896
He has to do it quickly.

1908
01:20:34,963 --> 01:20:36,865
Chef, please do it faster.

1909
01:20:36,932 --> 01:20:38,700
THE BYSTANDERS ARE MORE ANXIOUS
HOW WILL IT TURN OUT?

1910
01:20:38,767 --> 01:20:41,770
-Three. Two. One.
-Cheese!

1911
01:20:41,837 --> 01:20:42,938
Done!

1912
01:20:43,004 --> 01:20:45,040
Goodness, Chef Edward.

1913
01:20:45,106 --> 01:20:46,942
Wait, it's not for you.

1914
01:20:56,918 --> 01:21:01,723
Subtitle translation by: Eunsook Youn
